extends layout

block content

  div.container.text-center.content
    .row
      .col.mx-auto.my-5
       h1.display-4 Easily Generate and Store Secure Passwords
       p.lead Tired of trying to think up new passwords and then remembering them when you need to?
       p Worry no more! Simply sign up for a free account and let Password Generator look after it all for you.
       h3.mt-5 Why Register?
       p Registered users enjoy more options over their passwords than users who simply generate passwords on the home page.
       h3.mt-5 Added Benefits:
       ul.col-lg-6.offset-lg-3.benefits
         li.text-left <i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          p Choose password length
          li.text-left <i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>
           p Add "special characters" to your password
           li.text-left <i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            p Save passwords to your wallet so you never forget them
       a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href="/signup", role="button") Create Account
